 new friends or foes. Your decisions matter and will have a huge impact on the future of your species. Find hidden areas within hidden areas, easter eggs and 80s sci-fi legends...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/600510/extras/c9b982101ef896bacf658c5c137931d8.poster.avif?t=1729248618\" width=600 height=332 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/600510/extras/c9b982101ef896bacf658c5c137931d8.webm?t=1729248618\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/600510/extras/c9b982101ef896bacf658c5c137931d8.mp4?t=1729248618\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your clone is equipped with a Scanner that allows you to scan everything you'll find on your journey. Collected data will be stored in an in-game wiki and can be used to unlock upgrades, create advanced gear and to build & simulate your own Worlds once you've gained access to the betaverse.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/600510/extras/c264096b1461bb3a450d5853c9bf212a.avif?t=1729248618\" width=600 height=64 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fully customizable versatile Platformer Core</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Special Directional Gravity Shield Mechanics</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Huge Open World full of Secrets and Easter eggs</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fast Paced Combat with Free Aim or Aim Assist</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >RPG Mechanics, Quests and Inventory System</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Be good or evil - Dialogue & Karma System</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Companion Drones, Crafting & Survival Elements</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A wide variety of Weapon Types, tools, items and gadgets</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Scan & Rebuild Mechanics with InGame Wiki</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Driven by Rewarded Exploration and infinite Replayability.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/600510/extras/67bac134aac10e5fde35a7eb4799804e.avif?t=1729248618\" width=224 height=390 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>GINSHA</strong> is a one-man project by Adrian Zingg. Years of hard work, love and passion went into it. The Goal was to create something truly unique that remains in memory even years after completing it. The complete concept, realization, graphics and audio have been created exclusively for GINSHA.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/600510/extras/fd97337174e3efd882fb9262917db093.avif?t=1729248618\" width=600 height=170 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>GINSHA</strong> is best experienced with a gamepad or controller.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Let's connect - Join us on Discord!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
